  "title": "Sales Executive (Shipping)**Tiong Bahru**Up to $5K",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will promote the company’s shipping services by engaging potential and existing customers through calls and follow-ups, managing customer feedback, assisting with bookings, and ensuring timely delivery of shipping documents to meet monthly sales targets.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform cold calls and telemarketing to introduce and promote the company’s shipping services to potential customers</li><li>Follow up with sales leads and quotations to secure shipment bookings and increase sales</li><li>Monitor competitor activities to inform sales strategies and maintain competitive advantage</li><li>Respond to customer feedback and maintain positive relationships with existing and new customers to support customer retention</li><li>Assist in booking shipments when required to ensure smooth service delivery</li><li>Send bill of ladings to customers promptly to facilitate shipment processing</li><li>Achieve monthly sales targets by effectively managing sales activities and customer interactions</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Minimum <strong>2yrs sales experience in Freight Forwarding or Shipping industry</strong></li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>5 days work (9am to 6pm) </li><li>Tiong Bahru area</li><li><strong>Salary $3500 - $5000</strong></li><li>Transport allowance provided </li></ul>",
