    "description": "<p>Smart Forte Consulting LLP</p>\n<p>EA &nbsp;Licence: 17C8868 | Registration Number: R1108383 | Registration Number: R1108244</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At Smart Forte, it is our mission to help you find your dream job. Since 2004, we have been helping people like you, find their passion so that they will love their job. We have close relationships with companies from various industries, therefore providing you only the best available jobs. We specialise in permanent and contract recruitment solutions. Additionally, we offer career advise, comprehensive interview advise and consulting services.</p>\n<p>Our core values are the heart of our business. With over a decade of experience, we have a deep understanding of the markets and the people we work with, from candidates to clients. We are passionate about creating valuable relationships with everyone, and are committed to deliver our service offerings with the utmost professionalism and reliability.</p>",
